            </div>
<div class="blk blk_text blk-no-bg-lpm-449" id="f16038c80d5e487191a1981182089c3a" blk_class="blk_text" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-f16038c80d5e487191a1981182089c3a" > <div class="blk-data clearfix" font_ids="38"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color:#003399"><span style="font-size:36px"><span f_id="roboto_normal" f_uid="38" style="font-family:roboto; font-style:normal; font-weight:400">Питание</span></span></span></p></div> </div><div class="blk blk_text blk-no-bg-lpm-449" id="7e89d5b67d784f56bf255f4e8f1750b2" blk_class="blk_text" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-7e89d5b67d784f56bf255f4e8f1750b2" > <div class="blk-data clearfix" font_ids="16"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:20px"><span f_id="open_sans_normal" f_uid="16" style="font-family:open sans; font-style:normal; font-weight:400">На 2 этаже гостиницы - кафе с панорамным видом на Волгу.<br />Действует программа&nbsp;проживания с питанием -<br /><strong><span style="color:#FF0000">выгодный вариант для бизнес-путешественников!</span></strong><br />В отчетных докуметах информация о питании не указывается.</span></span></p></div> </div><div class="blk blk_ms skip-adapt" id="72cc725548ff479aa28b924e316f9984" blk_class="blk_ms" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-72cc725548ff479aa28b924e316f9984" data-tpl-id="1738" > <div class="block-content" ><div class="m-image__wrapper need-alignment" onclick="return msJsWrapper(event,'72cc725548ff479aa28b924e316f9984','reachGoals');"> <div class="m-image__sub-wrapper" onmouseenter="return msJsWrapper(event,'72cc725548ff479aa28b924e316f9984','showImgNotice');" onmouseleave="return msJsWrapper(event,'72cc725548ff479aa28b924e316f9984','hideImgNotice');"> <div class="m-image m-image--mob" data-page-link=""> <img src="//m-files.cdnvideo.ru/lpfile/3/8/1/381002eb59c043291541d2a29eed3cc7/-/crop/208x27x864x910/-/resize/348/-/quality/95/-/resize/1920/f.jpg?53756338" title="" alt="" loading="lazy"> </div> <div class="m-image m-image--pc" data-page-link=""> <img src="//m-files.cdnvideo.ru/lpfile/3/8/1/381002eb59c043291541d2a29eed3cc7/-/crop/0x26x1280x907/-/resize/902/-/quality/95/-/resize/1920/f.jpg?53756338" title="" alt="" loading="lazy"> </div> </div> </div></div> </div><div class="blk blk_box skip-adapt" id="4600338e52874c7aa1e84c252457908f" blk_class="blk_box" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-4600338e52874c7aa1e84c252457908f" > <div class="blk-data clearfix" ><div class="blk_box_self clearfix block-content" bg="#ffffff" data-is_border_allow="1" style="border:1.11111px solid rgb(204, 204, 204);padding:20px 20px;border-radius:5px;background:#ffffff;"> <div class="cell tpl_cell tpl_box_cell sortable_cell l_float " id="f22ec1431d4b4dbf8fc2649097fccae9" style="width: 100%;"> <div class="blk blk_text blk-no-bg-lpm-449" id="0580712de6514ed391c46a196c6d59da" blk_class="blk_text" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-0580712de6514ed391c46a196c6d59da" > <div class="blk-data clearfix" font_ids="38,42,40,18"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:28px"><span f_id="roboto_medium" f_uid="40" style="font-family:roboto,arial; font-style:normal; font-weight:500"><span style="color:#003399">Тариф ЗАВТРАК</span></span></span></p></div> </div><div blk_class="blk_container" class="blk_container v3 skip-adapt" id="9c3109234eb8463a9aff91ac221b0810" data-id="b-9c3109234eb8463a9aff91ac221b0810" type_id="" pos="20"> <div class="blk_container_cells_wrap"> <div class="blk_container_cells"> <div class="td_container_cell" cell_id="5d2b6a792f7647808ae5196d106b6cb3" data-cell_id="c-5d2b6a792f7647808ae5196d106b6cb3" >  <div class="cell v3 container_cell first_cell" id="5d2b6a792f7647808ae5196d106b6cb3" > <div class="blk blk_text blk-no-bg-lpm-449" id="2829ab5dfb2e47c29f62020beb6d4124" blk_class="blk_text" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-2829ab5dfb2e47c29f62020beb6d4124" > <div class="blk-data clearfix" font_ids="16"><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:24px"><font face="open sans"><span f_id="open_sans_normal" f_uid="16" style="font-family:open sans; font-style:normal; font-weight:400">от <strong><span style="color:#B22222">&nbsp;4 550&nbsp;руб./сутки</span></strong></span> за номер,</font></span></p></div> </div><div class="blk blk_text blk-no-bg-lpm-449" id="a5ef6d71568d4353a7781a6fbe0b2515" blk_class="blk_text" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-a5ef6d71568d4353a7781a6fbe0b2515" > <div class="blk-data clearfix" font_ids="16"><p style="text-align: inherit; font-size: inherit;"><span style="font-size:inherit; text-align:inherit"><span f_id="open_sans_normal" f_uid="16" style="font-family:open sans; font-size:inherit; font-style:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:inherit">в&nbsp;стоимость номера включен <span style="color:rgb(0, 51, 153); font-size:inherit; text-align:inherit">завтрак.</span></span></span></p><p style="text-align: inherit; font-size: inherit;"><span style="font-size:inherit; text-align:inherit"><span f_id="open_sans_normal" f_uid="16" style="font-family:open sans; font-size:inherit; font-style:normal; font-weight:400; text-align:inherit">Завтрак&nbsp;предоставляется в кафе гостиницы на 2 этаже<br />с 7.00&nbsp;до 10.00</span></span></p></div> </div><div class="blk blk_button skip-adapt" id="2c746bee9bb6459fbdc93ccb0e6e6cce" blk_class="blk_button" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-2c746bee9bb6459fbdc93ccb0e6e6cce" > <div class="blk-data clearfix" ><div class="blk_button_data_wrap "><a class="btn-new block-content " act="link" href="https://www.hotel-rossia.ru/?tl-booking-open=true&amp;tl-offer=47729" target="_blank" onclick="" data-action-name="link" style="">Забронировать</a></div></div> </div><div blk_class="blk_container" class="blk_container v3 skip-adapt" id="02c749c3f76d4a678e4262c3e19db605" data-id="b-02c749c3f76d4a678e4262c3e19db605" type_id="" pos="26"> <div class="blk_container_cells_wrap"> <div class="blk_container_cells"> <div class="td_container_cell" cell_id="8a770ae0f22e4f168b1b8c3b325af6e6" data-cell_id="c-8a770ae0f22e4f168b1b8c3b325af6e6" >  <div class="cell v3 container_cell first_cell" id="8a770ae0f22e4f168b1b8c3b325af6e6" > <div class="blk blk_ms skip-adapt" id="7cde1ddae2374b619d73458ef0884f63" blk_class="blk_ms" data-animation-class="" data-animation-duration="" data-animation-delay="" data-id="b-7cde1ddae2374b619d73458ef0884f63" data-tpl-id="1738" > <div class="block-content" ><div class="m-image__wrapper need-alignment" onclick="return msJsWrapper(event,'7cde1ddae2374b619d73458ef0884f63','reachGoals');"> <div class="m-image__sub-wrapper" onmouseenter="return msJsWrapper(event,'7cde1ddae2374b619d73458ef0884f63','showImgNotice');" onmouseleave="return msJsWrapper(event,'7cde1ddae2374b619d73458ef0884f63','hideImgNotice');"> <div class="m-image m-image--mob" data-page-link=""> <img src="//m-files-new.cdnvideo.ru/lpfile/1/b/4/1b497edf3dbfd00bd7ab7246d57ab5b5/-/crop/443x229x1032x983/-/resize/333/-/quality/95/-/resize/1920/f.jpg" title="" alt="" loading="lazy"> </div> <div class="m-image m-image--pc" data-page-link=""> <img src="//m-files-new.cdnvideo.ru/lpfile/1/b/4/1b497edf3dbfd00bd7ab7246d57ab5b5/-/crop/0x243x1920x953/-/resize/702/-/quality/95/-/resize/1920/f.jpg" title="" alt="" loading="lazy"> </div> </div> </div></div> </div> </div>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div>  </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div></div> </div>            </div>
